{"id":1579,"date":"2021-01-25T21:56:28","date_gmt":"2021-01-26T02:56:28","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/ccvcl.org\/?page_id=1579"},"modified":"2023-04-27T16:09:34","modified_gmt":"2023-04-27T20:09:34","slug":"data-structures-spring-2021","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/ccvcl.org\/data-structures-spring-2021\/","title":{"rendered":"Data Structures &#8211; Spring 2021"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>CSc21200&nbsp;Section EF&nbsp;Data Structures, Spring 2021, The City College of New York<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Instructor:<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong><br>TA<br>Class Meets:<br>Classroom:<\/strong><br><strong>Office Hours:<br>Office:<\/strong><br><strong>Email:<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Professor Zhigang&nbsp; Zhu<\/strong><br>n\/a<br>M,W&nbsp;&nbsp;2:00-3:40PM<br><strong>Online (<a href=\"https:\/\/ccny.zoom.us\/j\/563680171\">Class Zoom Link<\/a><\/strong>)<br>Wednesday:&nbsp; 4:00 pm &#8211; 5:00 pm<strong><br>Online Meeting (<a href=\"https:\/\/ccny.zoom.us\/j\/584248188\">Office Hour Zoom Link<\/a><\/strong>)<br><strong>Appointments<\/strong>: <a href=\"zzhu@ccny.cuny.edu\">zzhu@ccny.cuny.edu<\/a> <br>Assignment Submission: <strong><a href=\"mailto:ds.zhu.ccny@gmail.com\">ds.zhu.ccny@gmail.com<\/a><\/strong><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Course Update Information&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>02\/01\/2021. The first day of class<\/li><li>02\/01\/2021. <a href=\"http:\/\/ccvcl.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/CSc212-EF-Spring-2021-Quizzes.txt\">Grading for Quiz 1<\/a>.<\/li><li>02\/08\/2021. <a href=\"http:\/\/ccvcl.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/CSc212-EF-Spring-2021-Quizzes.txt\">Grading for Quizzes 1-2<\/a>.<\/li><li>02\/11\/2021. Updated <a href=\"http:\/\/ccvcl.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/CSc212-EF-Spring-2021-Quizzes.txt\">Grading for Quizzes 1-3<\/a>.<\/li><li>02\/16\/2021. <a href=\"http:\/\/ccvcl.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/CSc212